rComments: Professor Sullivan is by far one of the best professors I have ever had. Not only is she kind, personable and caring, she truly knows the subject manner. Her passion for teaching and humour make classes enjoyable and easy to pay attention to. I appreciated the variety of assignments and her expectations were super clear.

Highly recommend taking a class with Becky! She is kind, caring and approachable! Class content was interesting, there was 1 midterm (multiple choice), a paper and and exam (multiple choice). Plus in class assignments and reflections which where easy grade boosters. Overall I really enjoyed this class and she did a great time for her first class!

This is my first time writing a rate my prof review, but I felt compelled to do so given how much I enjoyed this class. I am so surprised that this semester was Professor Sullivan's first time teaching because she is truly a pro. Her lectures are incredibly engaging and her grading criteria is clear. Would strongly recommend this class with her.

She is such a nice prof! I never write any rate my prof reviews, but I came here to write one because she is such a great prof, and the lecture material is super interesting! She is also very understanding and responds very quickly if you have any questions about the assignment :) Overall, a great prof and class to take if you are considering it

Very nice prof, you can tell she cares about her students. She extended the deadline for the paper by several hours because she's aware that it's a busy time of the semester for us. Lectures were blended and recorded and the assignments and midterm were easy as long as you study the slides. Course material was very interesting to learn too.
